\begin_inset Formula ${\rm {\rm \text{Tr}}}\left(\widetilde{A_{jn}}\left(t\right)\widetilde{B_{j'n'}}\left(t\right)\right)={\rm {\rm {\rm \text{Tr}}}}\left(\widetilde{A_{jn}}\left(t\right)\right){\rm {\rm \text{Tr}}}\left(\widetilde{B_{j'n'}}\left(t\right)\right)$
